  "title": "Banking: Assistant Manager (Financial, Regulatory reporting & tax)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>*Seeking for an Accounts talent with minimum 5 years of experience handling Financial and Regulatory reporting in a Corporate Bank*</strong></em></p><p><strong>THE COMPANY</strong></p><p>This bank is reputable, stable and has a strong brand. Currently, they seek for an Assistant Manager to be part of their Finance team.</p><p><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul><li>Handle Financial, Statutory and Management reporting</li><li>Perform Regulatory/MAS reporting</li><li>Handle variances analysis</li><li>Perform Expenses processing and Nostro reconciliation</li><li>Involve in IT projects</li><li>Collaborate effectively with other internal and external stakeholders</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Accountancy/Commerce or ACCA or any other relevant education</li><li>Minimum 5 years of experience handling Financial and Regulatory reporting from a Corporate Bank</li><li>Diligent, solutions-oriented, team player, strong interpersonal and communication skills</li></ul><p>If you will like to explore this opportunity, please email your resume in Microsoft Word format to <a href=\"mailto:marie@resolutehunter.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">marie@resolutehunter.com</a></p><p>We thank you for your interest and will contact shortlisted candidates for more detailed discussion.</p><p>For more job openings, please visit our website at https://resolutehunter.com/opportunities/</p><p>EA Licence 18C9105</p><p>EA Reg R1105305</p>",
